            <title><![CDATA[歪歪歪！朋友们醒醒！教你#避免饭后犯困的三个方法# 👇🏻1⃣️首先你得少吃点[doge]吃得过饱容易增加胃肠的负担。2⃣️减少食物中的米饭、馒头、包子等碳水...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[歪歪歪！朋友们醒醒！教你<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E9%A5%AD%E5%90%8E%E7%8A%AF%E5%9B%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E9%A5%AD%E5%90%8E%E7%8A%AF%E5%9B%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#避免饭后犯困的三个方法#</span></a> 👇🏻<br><br>1⃣️首先你得少吃点<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>吃得过饱容易增加胃肠的负担。<br>2⃣️减少食物中的米饭、馒头、包子等碳水化合物的占比。<br>3⃣️犯困的时候按摩下太阳穴、风池穴、百会穴三个头部穴位，提神醒脑。（央视网）<br><br>你还有什么瞬间清醒小妙招？评论区分享<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[春游家族]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/2021_YoungFamily_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E7%8A%AF%E5%9B%B0%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E7%8A%AF%E5%9B%B0%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年轻人都容易犯困吗#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbya502ox9g2064078184.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
